trans-unit.source: Serves as a hash function for an <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.Headers.WarningHeaderValue" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 充当 <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.Headers.WarningHeaderValue" /> 对象的哈希函数。

trans-unit.source: A hash code for the current object.
trans-unit.target: 当前对象的哈希代码。

trans-unit.source: A hash code is a numeric value that is used to identify an object during equality testing.
trans-unit.target: 哈希代码是一个数字值，用于标识相等测试过程中的对象。

trans-unit.source: It can also serve as an index for an object in a collection.
trans-unit.target: 它还可以充当集合中的对象的索引。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.WarningHeaderValue.GetHashCode%2A> method is suitable for use in hashing algorithms and data structures such as a hash table.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.WarningHeaderValue.GetHashCode%2A>方法是适合在哈希算法和数据结构，如哈希表中使用。
